      <title>随着能源危机消退，嘉能可利润大幅下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/glencore-posts-steep-profit-fall-as-energy-crisis-fades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉能可公司 (Glencore Plc) 报告称，在市场从俄罗斯入侵乌克兰后带来巨额盈利的价格飙升和剧烈波动中回落后，利润大幅下降，并降低了股息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/glencore-posts-steep-profit-fall-as-energy-crisis-fades</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 07:03:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本田、马自达在年度劳工工资谈判中同意工会要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/honda-mazda-agree-to-union-demands-in-annual-labor-wage-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本田汽车公司和马自达汽车公司的经理们同意了工会提出的所有工资要求，并同意提高去年同期的薪酬，因为通货膨胀迫使日本企业向员工支付更高的工资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/honda-mazda-agree-to-union-demands-in-annual-labor-wage-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 07:00:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于大宗商品价格疲软，力拓利润下降 12%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/rio-tinto-s-full-year-profit-falls-12-to-11-8-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于大宗商品价格疲软和成本上升，力拓集团去年的基本利润下降了 12%，但该公司仍然设法支付了更高的股息。]]></description>
